column2: Melanoma Cells Subclustering of Single-cell Analysis SC22147

This is a subclustering analysis of single-cell analysis SC22147. For this subclustering analysis cells from theMelanoma (C3), and Melanoma_2 cluster (C13) in experiment SC22147 were selected from sample groups LiverMetM3, SubcutM3 and SubcutNoLiverMetM2. In this selection, sample LiverMetM3R2 featured only 10 cells and was excluded from this subclustering analysis.
